      <title>耶伦表示中国关税不会导致美国物价大幅上涨</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/china-tariffs-won-t-increase-us-prices-janet-yellen-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国财政部长珍妮特·耶伦表示，对中国商品征收新关税将保护美国企业和工人，而不会刺痛美国消费者的钱包。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/china-tariffs-won-t-increase-us-prices-janet-yellen-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 23:22:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>监管机构称英国人等待英国税务当局处理税务事宜已长达 798 年</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/brits-spend-798-years-on-hold-to-uk-tax-authority-watchdog-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据政府支出监管机构称，上一财年，英国客户向该国税务机关扣留的时间总计近 800 年，目前有超过一半的电话无人接听。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/brits-spend-798-years-on-hold-to-uk-tax-authority-watchdog-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 23:01:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科恩表示特朗普知道支票是为了封口费而不是合法工作</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/cohen-says-trump-knew-checks-were-for-hush-money-not-legal-work</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周二，唐纳德·特朗普的律师对迈克尔·科恩进行了缓慢的盘问，后者试图推翻他之前的证词，即他参与了一项封口费计划，以帮助这位前总统影响 2016 年大选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/cohen-says-trump-knew-checks-were-for-hush-money-not-legal-work</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 22:14:15 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>委内瑞拉考虑撤回对欧盟选举监督员的邀请</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/venezuela-weighs-withdrawing-invitation-to-eu-election-monitors</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟暂停对政府官员的部分但并非全部制裁后，委内瑞拉可能会撤回对欧盟监督总统选举的邀请。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-05-14/venezuela-weighs-withdrawing-invitation-to-eu-election-monitors</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 14 May 2024 22:06:41 GMT</pubDate>
